{"tid":1459692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實封機場都絕，連有錢佬都走唔到","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:37:26.000Z","uid":271875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8469e2a056d5fcc76a84579afea7cdc626a52e0b","tid":1459692,"uid":271875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:10.000Z","msg":"日日封機場，有錢既都要企我地呢邊要同政府講數！<br />\n佢哋都諗香港有咩，有外國國籍一飛就走，反正錢已轉走左。但依家機場唔安全，有咩事會停飛，無左個逃生口。<br />\n共產黨有咩解放軍管香港，第一時間要禁止啲錢唔比走，捉住班有錢人做人質，你睇逃犯修例一出，大劉即走去加拿大就知佢地幾驚。<br />\n佢哋考慮到自己人生安全，一係邊朝一通返就即走，一係就要政府談判，放返個緊急逃生口機場。<br />\n所以今輔未有方式應對呢次攬抄攻勢。<br />\n同埋呢輔和理非就夠，唔駛用劍既。"},{"pid":"917a7ef7a1de090ef3ca096414ef1ead3013e071","tid":1459692,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:17:10.000Z","msg":"Is it possible to get in the departure hall with a fake air ticket?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://keyflight.io/fake\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkeyflight.io%2Ffake&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=ef97ad27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://keyflight.io/fake</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.returnflights.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.returnflights.net%2F&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f3a21ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.returnflights.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://techiestechguide.com/fake-airline-ticket/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechiestechguide.com%2Ffake-airline-ticket%2F&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=5d884a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://techiestechguide.com/fake-airline-ticket/</a>"},{"pid":"1992513570aa2110b4421b01cc269097c1ce2cce","tid":1459692,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:37:26.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k